    effortless-ntwf:comment "Generates the post-deployment health report by summarizing telemetry after a release. A role, not an identity — currently filled by the DeploymentHealth-AI agent (health-summarizer-v1.2.0), it could be reassigned to a human or a newer model without changing the workflow structure. Its RoleAssignments history records an earlier human-reviewer period and the agent-type transitions." ;
    effortless-ntwf:hasCapability effortless-ntwf:cap-risk-analysis ;
    effortless-ntwf:filledByAIAgent effortless-ntwf:ntwf-health-ai ;
    effortless-ntwf:ownedBy effortless-ntwf:ntwf-engineering .

